name: Unlimited imagination - metaverse.01
description: We can create our own metaverse, customize according to what we imagine. We just think about it and then everything happens instantly. What we think, what we want, for example we want to be the strongest king even though we are chickens. Then he will answer according to the original physical condition and our imagination. This is what my version of the metaverse looks like. Just keep dreaming because imagination is more powerful than knowledge.
